_sText:
A map made by Hamster, requested by me. My clan is having a knife tournament and needed a map, and Hamster was the guy I turned to for it. I must say he came through for us :D Everyone that has played on it so far likes it, so I thought it would be an appropriate release.

10 spawns a side, if you jump off the platform the water kills you.

Many thanks to Hamster for doing this, and for permission to release it :D
